*this one is the inverse of the fx_to_2point*
*convert 2 points to a function*
*in reallity the a and b of ax + b*

xa reel
ya reel
                *input of the ... not programmer*
xb reel
yb reel

a reel
b reel

DEBUT:
    AFFICHER("Xa = ") *point A*
    LIRE(xa)
    AFFICHER("Ya = ")
    LIRE(ya)

    AFFICHER("Xb = ")
    LIRE(xb)
    AFFICHER("Yb = ")
    LIRE(yb)

    a <- (yb - ya) / (xb - xa)

    b <- ya - a * xa
    AFFICHER("The value of a is ")
    AFFICHER a
    AFFICHER("The value of b is ")
    AFFICHER b
    AFFICHER("the function is yet ax + b")

